com.wx.console

Class UserConsoleInterface

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.wx.console.UserConsoleInterface
  • Direct Known Subclasses:
    JLineUCI

    public class UserConsoleInterface
extends java.lang.Object
    This class implements an interactive console interface with the user and allows to input different type of data from the user.
